  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK1032">
<l>uḻuvā rulakattārk kāṇiyaḵ tāṟṟār </l>
<l>toḻuvārē yellām poṟuttu</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Agriculturists are (as it were) the linch-pin of the world for they support all other workers who cannot till the soil.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
